# Scraper + cron
S core web /api
Sc products https://example.com/products list=.product title=h2 price=.price
Sc prices https://prices.example.com table=#rates rate=td:nth-child(2)

Cr L1 */15 * * * *
L1: R api.G /scrape/products ->res J res

Cr L2 0 */1 * * *
L2: R api.G /scrape/prices ->rates J rates

E /scrape/products G ->L1
E /scrape/prices G ->L2

Q scrape 500 3
C scrape_cache url 1800
